method.name: get_value
method.description: Returns the value the iterator is pointing. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]

method.name: is_null
method.description: Returns [code]true[/code] if iterator points to null, [code]false[/code] if not [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]

method.name: next
method.description: The iterator points to the previous value to the left, if there is no value to the left, it points to null. Returns itself. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]

method.name: prev
method.description: The iterator points to the next value to the right, if there is no value to the right, it points to null. Returns itself. [b]Complexity:[/b] [i]O(1)[/i]
